          circular vertical support, which is in turn connected to a screw-on cap. Within the metal
          casing there are top and bottom plastic inserts made from <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">PMMA</ENAMEX>. <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">Fluids</ENAMEX> are introduced to
          and drained out of the flow cell through integrated stainless <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">steel</ENAMEX> tubing within the
