          Image <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Analysis</ENAMEX>
          Images were analyzed using a custom algorithm supported by <ENAMEX TYPE="EVENT">Image-Pro Plus</ENAMEX> (<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Media</ENAMEX>
